| Version 2.12  (? ? 2006)                                              |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| Version 2.11  (1 July 2006)                                              |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  - Do not rely on external data
  - Fix timer to work with SDL when nothing else succeeds

o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| Version 2.8  (29. August 2002)                                              |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  - Completely revamped the automake/autoconf setup.


o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| Version 2.7 (5. January 2002)                                               |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  - Fixed a bug in the parsing of the model configuration file. (Thanks to
    Nick Edgington and Ladislav Stefun!)


o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| Version 0.6 (4. August 2001)                                                |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  - Modified the material/texture-handling to the new cal3d library style.
  - Changed the rendering loop to work with the new rendering API of the cal3d
    library.
  - Implemented a LOD (level-of-detail) slider-control.
  - The demo loads "standard" cal3d model configuration files now.


o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| Version 0.5 (5. May 2001)                                                   |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  - Included the 'paladin' model from Doug showing the new texture-mapping
    support of cal3d.


o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o
| Version 0.0 (10. April 2001)                                                |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------o

  - "The Cally Demo" project kick off.


